title: Eurythmics - Sweet Dreams [1983] DVD5
description: Eurythmics - Sweet Dreams [1983] DVD5 Filmed at Heaven, one of London's hottest clubs in 1983, the Eurythmics striking stage presence is complimented by a spectacular laser show.The concert is only part of the story. included in 'Sweet Dreams (The Video Album)' are video clips of 'Sweet Dreams', 'Love Is A Stranger' and 'Who's That Girl'. Tying it all together is animated footage created specifically for the show. This extraordinary video features in-concert performances from 1983, conceptual video clips and animation woven together in a fabulous "album" highlighting Eurythmics international smash hit "Sweet Dreams" and more.
